title: Solana falls below 10$
content: Solana dropped below 10 dollars for the first time since 2021.

title: DeGods is moving to Ethereum
content:
Dust Labs decided to leave solana.
DeGods is migrating to Ethereum & Yoots is moving to Polygon.

title: Solana drops to 14$
content: With the fall of FTX, the biggest supporter of solana is gone, and solana is soaring.

title: Google cloud becomes a solana validator
content: Google cloud announced they will host solana validators.
